subject: NCAA Volleyball Championships
Volleyball
Colleges and Universities
lead_paragraph: Rachael Kidder had 21 kills, and U.C.L.A. advanced to its first national championship match since 1991 with a sweep of Florida State in the N.C.A.A. women’s semifinals.
